    <mainBody>
      <paragraph eId="para_1" class="MercuryDocument">
        <content eId="para_1__content">
          <p xml:space="preserve"> At its 63rd plenary meeting, on 21 March 2024, the General Assembly, on the proposal of its President, decided, without setting a precedent, to invite the Assistant Secretary-General for Human Rights, Ilze Brand Kehris, the Chair of the Committee on the Elimination of Racial Discrimination, Verene Albertha Shepherd, the Chair-designate of the Permanent Forum on People of African Descent, June Soomer, and and the founder and Chief Executive Officer of Advancing Health Equity, Uché Blackstock, to make statements at the commemorative meeting on the occasion of the International Day for the Elimination of Racial Discrimination.</p>
        </content>
